game.description:
Hey friends! Is not exciting to kill dangerous worms by putting your intense shooting abilities to test? Join Worms Combat Coop game and get ready to enter an area that is full of deadly worms! The best part is that you also have a weapon to deal with these dangerous enemies so you do not need to bother about anything at all. Your quick reflexes and abilities to handle the gun perfectly will definitely get you through all the hurdles and clean the forest from these uninvited guests. 
Use your gun and fight against these big and disgusting worms like never before in a strange forest in this one of highly challenging adventure games for boys! There are several playability options to explore. Try out the adventure challenge or create your own map in a level generator or get a pleasure of editing all the stats of the character in a test cheating arena! The gameplay of this cool html4 war game is pretty interesting and you can make it the endless through your skill of destroying all the worms. 
So how long can you stand either alone or with your buddy? Have fun in the open world.
Play solo mode or invite your friend on the same keyboard on one computer in this two players game! Try to be attentive and kill all the worms you see in the forest! Do not forget to collect coins on your way in this multiplayer endless worms game. You can use those coins to purchase new weapons and make his more powerful than before. This cooperate free online game features multiple weapons, endless gameplay and level generator. Check out more 2 player games here on atmegame.com, no download required!!
